  <title translate="true">MotionDesigner-Period-Ratio</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword translate="true">Motion Design Considerations:<keyword translate="true">Dynamic Performance</keyword><keyword translate="true">Natural Frequency</keyword><keyword translate="true">Period Ratio of the Cam Follower</keyword></keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1" style="width:500px;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">In this context,</text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true"> Period</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> relates to a</text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true"> time-period</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Period-Ratio</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">: the ratio of two time-periods in a mechanical system: </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Period-Ratio = Period-of-motion / Period-of-fundamental vibration</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Period-Ratio</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> varies with the machine-speed.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Aim to keep the </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Period Ratio &gt; 10</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Period Ratio &gt; 10</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> - High Stiffness / Inertia Ratio. Slow-Speed M/c.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Period-Ratio &lt; 5</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> - Low Stiffness / Inertia ratio, High-Speed M/c.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
  </body>
